::DrillBit::

DrillBit brought his thought back to what was around him, only to see
KitKat and Testifer argue, and KK run out. He walked up to Testifer.
"If you cause her more grief, then she already has.., I'll drown you,
ina pit of molten lava. Stay away from her, you bastard." He says,
running out after her.
"I know it hurts. I know you will have to live with this." He came up to
her, and hugged her.
"And I am so sorry."

::K-9::

K-9 woke up, in the forest. He started running again.

::Hot Rod::

"I'm going to the mess hall, to get something to eat. You two want to
come?" He askes, ArcAngel and Kamodia.
